{"tid":2427152,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王百羽: 香港人要行嘅路點都要行落去, 大家唔需要傷春悲秋","createTime":"2021-02-28T14:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T01:25:06.000Z","uid":134071,"like":70,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2fa3fc50a199df4833217f8996b444459cb2c019","tid":2427152,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:49:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/henrywongpakyu/posts/1820680008107402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhenrywongpakyu%2Fposts%2F1820680008107402&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3f2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=6ccab398\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/henrywongpakyu/posts/1820680008107402</a><br />\n<br />\n王百羽 Henry Wong - 王伯<br />\n10 小時  &middot;<br />\n<br />\n大家唔需要傷春悲秋<br />\n香港人要行嘅路點都要行落去<br />\n做一個好的人，阻止錯的事，為未來做對的事"},{"pid":"72fea01baad960b8e68be1abdb3103bf6ecdc43c","tid":2427152,"uid":134071,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:50:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3941300692622188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fposts%2F3941300692622188&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3f2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=7102e893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3941300692622188</a><br />\n<br />\nStand News 立場新聞<br />\n <br />\n7 小時  &middot;<br />\n【王百羽到天水圍警署報到】<br />\n五十多名民主派初選參與人，上月被指控違反國安法被捕，今天被要求「提前報到」，外界預料他們或將被落案起訴及即時還柙。<br />\n<br />\n超區參選人、元朗區議員王百羽下午與朋友到場時，表現平靜，形容自己當初參政時早有心理準備，又指已買了沒有鞋帶的新鞋、準備帶一套《涼宮春日》漫畫進去看，笑言「有排睇」，但他沒有選擇帶膠框眼鏡來，因為「未知最後會點」，認為還有機會保釋出來。<br />\n<br />\n王百羽其後在警署門外徘徊，等待至 2 時報到前的最後一刻，與一眾朋友相擁、拍膊頭，然後拿起紙巾擦走眼框淚光。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>他最後寄語支持者，「要問心無愧，唔係叫你做個乖巧嘅人，而係要繼續做個好人，去阻止錯嘅嘢發生」。</strong>"},{"pid":"53ab211f9fde521f9ac97bfa2e626e52c1ce5057","tid":2427152,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17f43430e8bea5d0476ceca8c45c2070e28051b","tid":2427152,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068b9c22c5d74b271abc154d1164785b2645eca3","tid":2427152,"uid":279463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45154564bf2cff62194a76ffe858e5b1af46fdb3","tid":2427152,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27533f704f4cb0a9f8fd4619fd72f9b51719661d","tid":2427152,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"068b9c22c5d74b271abc154d1164785b2645eca3","tid":2427152,"uid":279463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.